You do have promptsubst set, don't you?

What about

PROMPT='%{^[[5;46m%}%m:%l %T %~${PROJECT:+
%{^[[31m[%\}}$PROJECT${PROJECT:+]%{^[[30m%\}}%#%{^[[0m%}'

(note, that `}' in %} are quoted). This seems to work. I suspect, why it
happens, but I do not know code good enugh.

